reviewText: These scenes from their top rated Nashville Network show is an indication of their humor and, ability to work together for over 40 years with only one member change. That was due to Lou DeWitt's terminal illness. They showed the same wit and musical range that got them started with Johnny Cash and sustained them through their career and well earned retirement. Statler fans will enjoy as should country and quartet listeners.
